{"title":"「网络流 24 题」魔术球","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/321#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=321","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/321/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/321/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/321"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"假设有 $ n $ 根柱子，现要按下述规则在这 $ n $ 根柱子中依次放入编号为 $ 1, 2, 3, 4, \\cdots $ 的球。\r\n\r\n1. 每次只能在某根柱子的最上面放球。\r\n2. 在同一根柱子中，任何 $ 2 $ 个相邻球的编号之和为完全平方数。\r\n\r\n试设计一个算法，计算出在 $ n $ 根柱子上最多能放多少个球。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"文件第 $ 1 $ 行有 $ 1 $ 个正整数 $ n $，表示柱子数。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行是球数。接下来的 $ n $ 行，每行是一根柱子上的球的编号。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n4\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n11\r\n1 8\r\n2 7 9\r\n3 6 10\r\n4 5 11\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$ 1 \\leq n \\leq 55 $"}]}